data.description: Don't Miss this Beautiful End Condo Unit located near Kempsville and Greenbrier! This home features 2beds & 2.5baths with an open & flexible floor plan. Upstairs you'll find the Two Primary En-suites with a 3rd flex space bedroom that can be used as a workout room, office, man cave, or anything else you need extra space for. The Kitchen has been recently updated with a new microwave, stackable washer/dryer & Refrigerator! The floors have been updated with New LVP Flooring & the bathrooms have been updated with newer vanities. Enjoy the private patio or a stroll through the nearby City View Park. Condo Fee includes water, sewer, trash, ground maintenance & two pools. Just minutes away from Shopping, Interstates, Bases, Regent University & Schools! Schedule your Private Showing Today!
